    "The software tool VOS viewer was employed to generate the keyword co-occurrence network.",
    "A \"minimum number of occurrences\" criterion was established to achieve an optimal network, requiring a keyword to appear at least four times before inclusion in the network.",
    "Out of the initial pool of 572, we selected 51 keywords.",
    "This ensured an optimal and easily reproducible network while maintaining readability.",
    "Figure 7 illustrates the co-occurrence network of keywords."
